\'Medium\', \'Well Done\']\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'sh_ribeye\',\n        name: \'Bone-In Cowboy Ribeye\',\n        description: \'Tender, richly marbled 18oz ribeye, aged for 35 days, served with custom peppercorn cream sauce.\',\n        price: 45.00,\n        customizationOptions: [\'Medium Rare\', \'Medium\', \'Medium Well\']\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'sh_truffle_burger\',\n        name: \'Double Truffle Burger\',\n        description: \'Double wagyu beef patties, melted black truffle white cheddar, crisp arugula, and garlic aioli on a toasted brioche bun.\',\n        price: 18.50,\n        customizationOptions: [\'Extra cheese\', \'No onions\', \'Gluten-free bun\']\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'sh_caesar\',\n        name: \'Classic Caesar with Grilled Steak\',\n        description: \'Crisp romaine lettuce, fresh shaved parmigiano-reggiano, hand-rolled sourdough croutons, tossed in garlic anchovy emulsion, topped with prime sliced sirloin.\',\n        price: 19.00\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'sh_mac_cheese\',\n        name: \'Lobster Macaroni & Cheese\',\n        description: \'Campanelle pasta baked in a creamy five-cheese mornay sauce with chunks of cold water Atlantic lobster tail and finished with herbed panko crust.\',\n        price: 22.00\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \'urban_bites\',\n    name: \'Urban Bites\',\n    tags: [\'Burgers\', \'Fries\', \'Fast Casual\'],\n    rating: 4.6,\n    deliveryTime: \'15-25 min\',\n    deliveryTimeValue: 20,\n    distance: 1.1,\n    deliveryFee: 1.99,\n    isFreeDelivery: false,\n    discount: \'15% Off\',\n    image: \'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA4jPmsOW8BKn873nl6iulEAGQL68SalnXdDBpixzUU5q4QjwpCkuvx4l2EkjUb1d2LjLDtBasc3MyvpIGeyRWdPTYI7SfIAE0SfBaMV1kC225DGbTGKp3sTGJmMVgty20fJ04Lj43xiUc2D4ODVrufxfTl_MBkqlwHAw_G3Ikiu5ac78s5VoZQLC_nrle09lwVrWFiVPLBYnPVsl4qcgLC6ztuNbnK_sCiX-wmaadjLRrrvI6BrdmvLb93XtoTZ3EQydhVnTgzaiI\',\n    menu: [\n      {\n        id: \'ub_double_cheese\',\n        name: \'Urban Double Cheeseburger\',\n        description: \'Two smashed grass-fed beef patties, double American cheese, caramelized onions, house pickles, and secret Smash Sauce on potato roll.\',\n        price: 13.99,\n        customizationOptions: [\'Extra cheese\', \'Add bacon\', \'No onions\', \'Lettuce wrap\']\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'ub_crispy_chicken\',\n        name: \'Hot Crispy Chicken Sandwich\',\n        description: \'Buttermilk-brined double fried chicken thigh tossed in Nashville hot oil, sweet tangy pickle chips, and creamy slaw on brioche.\',\n        price: 12.50,\n        customizationOptions: [\'Mild\', \'Medium\', \'Xtra Hot\']\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'ub_truffle_fries\',\n        name: \'Parmesan Truffle Fries\',\n        description: \'Crisp hand-cut Russet potatoes, white truffle oil, grated pecorino, and fresh parsley, served with house garlic dipping sauce.\',\n        price: 6.99\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'ub_milkshake\',\n        name: \'Gourmet Salted Caramel Shake\',\n        description: \'Slow-churned premium vanilla bean gelato blended with homemade sea salted caramel sauce and fresh farm cream, capped with whipped cream.\',\n        price: 5.50\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \'pasta_fresca\',\n    name: \'Pasta Fresca\',\n    tags: [\'Italian\', \'Handmade Pasta\', \'Vegetarian Friendly\'],\n    rating: 4.9,\n    deliveryTime: \'30-40 min\',\n    deliveryTimeValue: 35,\n    distance: 3.7,\n    deliveryFee: 2.99,\n    isFreeDelivery: false,\n    image: \'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuArgDIL9KLzq5ZsApELWgYS3y8HQs9wSVxxHf8FHKmyqQhnzEAa3rvvaUUNQa5AYYgYehaggp8vqVC6IlXc697ltid9krYc8SUQxTRWEOI1BhMvYDHSnQP8ifgFllVkfqAda8OdbUhS2drUJO4O6JLWXW0JRxP_A3D0Ux1twYAwdJjId72SupMxUtW7IbyggYamrivoWy093ntQyoknBK6sIWoezFNdTnxijcuVsYafPQILAyhxunA-LeW5bCFyLrMaGBb_rGMvU0Q\',\n    menu: [\n      {\n        id: \'pf_fettuccine\',\n        name: \'Handmade Fettuccine Alfredo\',\n        description: \'Fettuccine kneaded from organic semolina and pasture egg yolk, cooked al dente in a rich emulsion of authentic parmigiano-reggiano and sweet sweet butter.\',\n        price: 18.99,\n        customizationOptions: [\'Add grilled chicken\', \'Add prawns\', \'Gluten-free noodles\']\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'pf_lasagna\',\n        name: \'Grandma\342\200\231s Bolognese Lasagna\',\n        description: \'Fresh pasta sheets layered with slow-simmered 8-hour beef & veal rag\303\271, creamy bechamel, and melted whole-milk mozzarella.\',\n        price: 21.00\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'pf_tiramisu\',\n        name: \'House Signature Tiramisu\',\n        description: \'Light ladyfingers soaked in robust espresso and sweet dark rum, layered with whipped organic mascarpone custard, dusted liberally with direct-trade cocoa.\',\n        price: 8.50\n      },\n      {\n        id: \'pf_burrata\',\n        name: \'Creamy Heirloom Burrata Salad\',\n        description: \'Pugliese burrata bulb surrounded by heirloom cherry tomatoes, wild arugula, extra virgin olive oil drizzle, aged balsamic glaze, and fresh pine nut pesto.\',\n        price: 14.50\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \'miyabi_sushi\',\n    name: \'Miyabi Sushi\',\n    tags: [\'Japanese\', \'Seafood\', \'Authentic\'],\n    rating: 4.7,\n    deliveryTime: \'40-50 min\',\n    deliveryTimeValue: 45,\n    distance: 4.2,\n    deliveryFee: 3.50,\n    isFreeDelivery: false,\n    image: \'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCR50Ht2X1Mwfs1wwMxi8XFT5HsY1AvQuN5ET_BVWNR5pbrkeDcKDHv-kOPsdRu4JJIWq2itatHkpGMBN2Krppu1yvVN551DQF8ag8-Jz1y65o9OwxhibwTBjWxKoMbEG0Go2t7TsMF_JMb2q9p8TVPfjCJxnbLsLhulhVW87uYs1moahSKWywnZR9dGA8GNxV2cavxL34efzr50YQ2ef9c2z5K8NddwlLkCkLp4wsQmkfNOL1CiQUKURKUFnwlvA21rd9lYEWv0eI\',\n    menu: [\n      {\n        id: \'ms_omakase\',\n        name: \'Premium Sushi Omakase Set\',\n        description: \'A curated chef selection of 8 nigiri sushi pieces (tuna belly, king salmon, r