    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/Navbar.tsx` to handle responsive navigation. It will render the high-end desktop header with fine typography and buttons on larger viewports, and switch to a mobile header with bottom navigation bar (Home, Orders, Search, Profile) on smaller screens. This matches the exact visual specs of the desktop and mobile prototypes."
