    modified_response: "I will now create `/src/components/CartScreen.tsx` which manages the user\'s shopping basket and checkout preferences:\n1. Dynamic Cart items list with increase/decrease controllers.\n2. Address component showing \"Home, 4522 Business District, Skyline Towers, Apt 4B\" with inline edit capability.\n3. Interactive Payment selector supporting Stripe card payment and UPI options.\n4. Calculated cost summaries (Subtotal, dynamic Delivery Fees, Taxes & Service Charges, final Total).\n5. \"Place Order\" button that submits the cart, creates a simulated active order, and routes the user straight to the live \"Order Tracking\" dashboard."
