  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing Order Tracking UI**\n\nI\'m currently focused on the UI for order `#ZY-8821`, specifically the `OrderTracking.tsx` component. The header is planned, featuring a back button, the order number, and a support agent icon. I\'ve started the mock map section design, intending it to be interactive and detailed.\n\n\n**Refining Interactive Elements**\n\nI\'ve been further developing the interactive elements. My focus is on making the map and delivery agent details truly engaging. I\'ve integrated animated progress bars and updated estimated delivery times with live simulations. Now, a \"Trigger Live Tracker Simulation\" button will make this UI come to life.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/OrderTracking.tsx` which maps the live order tracking workflow for order `#ZY-8821`:\n1. Clean navigational headers and status trackers.\n2. An interactive tracking map with positioned visual markers for the customer\'s Home, the Restaurant, and the moving Delivery Agent.\n3. Live Simulation Controls so developers and users can run a time-lapse, watch the agent move, trigger status step transitions, and read simulated message feeds from agent Marcus Rodriguez.\n4. Quick actions like \"Call Marcus\" and a conversational mockup chat overlay.\n5. Dynamic order summary matching the items selected during the checkout phase."
